org.cougaar.mts.base
Class SocketDelegateImplBase

java.lang.Object
  java.net.Socket
      org.cougaar.mts.base.SocketDelegateImplBase

public abstract class SocketDelegateImplBase
extends java.net.Socket

This class is a delegating Socket that simply passes all methods to another socket. It's handy as a base class for Socket aspect delegates, as attached by the SocketFactory.
